1
00:01:38,180 --> 00:01:41,789
[FEUD]

2
00:01:42,130 --> 00:01:45,080
[Episode 28]

3
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:57,600
[Temple of the Primordial God]

4
00:02:01,970 --> 00:02:02,780
Xingman!

5
00:02:08,870 --> 00:02:10,729
Xingman, what are you doing here?

6
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,400
I've looked all over for you.

7
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:24,840
Xingman, what's wrong?

8
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,470
I miss home.

9
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:39,720
You don't have to
stay here to keep me company.

10
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:42,460
You can return to the Yinlian Sect first.

11
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,990
After I wrap things up here,

12
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,450
I'll go find you.

13
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:49,170
When will that be?

14
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,079
How long do I have to wait for you to take

15
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:52,540
the initiative to find me?

16
00:02:54,430 --> 00:02:57,110
Xingman, once this matter is settled,

17
00:02:57,410 --> 00:02:59,340
I will definitely go back with you.

18
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:03,590
You have responsibilities you can't shirk

19
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:05,800
and your master and fellows
you can't leave behind.

20
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:08,150
Yet to me, you always say,

21
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:10,520
"Wait, wait, and wait a bit more."

22
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:15,240
Meng Chu,

23
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:18,360
all I want is you.

24
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,960
Why can't you want me only?

25
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,700
I'll ask you one more time.

26
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:30,400
Are you going with me or not?

27
00:03:45,310 --> 00:03:45,960
Xingman,

28
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:48,680
don't be mad.

29
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:54,950
Be patient.

30
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:05,730
My mother said,

31
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:10,400
"A man who won't
take the initiative to find you

32
00:04:11,130 --> 00:04:12,460
is not worth courting."

33
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:16,720
I'll give you two days
to think it through.

34
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:19,920
I'm returning to the Yinlian Sect
the day after tomorrow.

35
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,570
Come with me or not,

36
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:25,160
whatever.

37
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,250
Xingman.

38
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:56,560
[Temple of the Primordial God]

39
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:15,500
My Lord, don't scare me.

40
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:20,420
I can't find my wife again.

41
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,850
Where did she go this time?

42
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:27,000
Can you take me to find her?

43
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,230
Please!

44
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,830
Bai Jiusi,
you're already long in the tooth.

45
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,360
Stop pretending to be a kid.

46
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:38,340
Shame on you.

47
00:05:39,450 --> 00:05:41,050
Do you know where my wife is?

48
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:46,970
Bai Jiusi, do you remember who I am?

49
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:57,600
How about this? Call me big bro,

50
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,770
and I'll take you to find your wife.

51
00:06:00,450 --> 00:06:01,940
Don't bully His Lordship.

52
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,480
My Lord,

53
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:07,630
I'm taking you to Her Ladyship.

54
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:13,910
My Lady, His Lordship was whining
to meet you.

55
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:15,400
Or he wouldn't go to bed.

56
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,130
I really had no choice

57
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,360
but to bring him here.

58
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:25,790
Well, then, My Lady, I'm taking my leave.

59
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,530
Call me if you and His Lordship
need anything.

60
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,840
Is it fun?

61
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:53,520
It's fun just to see you, darling.

62
00:06:57,970 --> 00:06:59,659
Is it fun to play dumb?

63
00:07:00,660 --> 00:07:01,730
Bai Jiusi,

64
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:04,050
you think pretending to forget
everything from the past

65
00:07:04,050 --> 00:07:05,980
can really let bygones be bygones?

66
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,870
Listen, it's impossible.

67
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:13,430
Too much has happened between us.

68
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,270
There's no way to forget

69
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,980
and no way to start over!

70
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:29,080
Darling,

71
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:32,290
did I do something wrong

72
00:07:33,490 --> 00:07:34,830
and upset you?

73
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:51,760
Please don't leave me behind again.

74
00:07:54,210 --> 00:07:57,250
Bai Jiusi, what on earth
are you trying to do?

75
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:11,370
I only want to be with you.

76
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:57,080
Master.

77
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:01,070
What brings you here?

78
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:08,910
I heard that Heavenly Lord Dacheng
came to lodge in your place.

79
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,860
So I came to drop in on you, Master.

80
00:09:13,810 --> 00:09:17,140
You're worried I can't let go of my hatred
and might hurt him?

81
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:23,160
You're always the most sensible one.
So there's no need to worry about that.

82
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:28,150
I'm actually concerned about
how you feel inside, Master.

83
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:37,550
Have you ever had a crush on someone?

84
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:45,440
There was once
during my days in seclusion.

85
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,700
Since my seclusion kicked off,

86
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:57,440
I've often caught the fragrance of flowers
drifting into the cave.

87
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,240
I didn't pay much attention to it

88
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,000
until one time...

89
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:48,640
At that moment,
I wanted to open my eyes and take a look.

90
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:54,900
I'm a coward.

91
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:59,220
I fell for someone
but didn't dare to tell him.

92
00:11:00,090 --> 00:11:01,610
I only had the guts

93
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:05,880
to secretly leave a bouquet
at his doorstep every few days.

94
00:11:07,510 --> 00:11:09,410
I picked all the flowers

95
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,360
on Yufan Mountain.

96
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:17,550
Then I started traveling around,

97
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:21,320
leaving new flowers at his door
whenever I found some.

98
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:24,130
I kept drinking all day long,

99
00:11:24,760 --> 00:11:27,600
hoping that alcohol could
help me pluck up my courage

100
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,030
and tell him my feelings for him

101
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:30,680
the next time we met.

102
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:37,970
Unfortunately, I'm uniquely gifted.

103
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:40,340
The more I drink, the more sober I become.

104
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:43,550
It doesn't help me
summon up courage at all.

105
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:51,190
Did you open your eyes to see?

106
00:11:57,670 --> 00:12:00,960
No, I gave up later.

107
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:05,320
Some stuff's better left in the dark.

108
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:10,040
I was in seclusion
with unfinished responsibilities

109
00:12:10,530 --> 00:12:13,830
and didn't want to mess up someone's life.

110
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:19,310
Did you later find out
who was sending you flowers?

111
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,560
Yes, I did.

112
00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:23,030
She once asked me

113
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:26,250
about my favorite flower.

114
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:30,290
Master Xuan Wei,
do you have any favorite flowers?

115
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:34,390
I don't like flowers.

116
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,470
Dandelions are not bad though.

117
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,220
I see.

118
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,460
Sorry.

119
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:57,920
It was my own choice
and had nothing to do with you, Master.

120
00:12:58,270 --> 00:13:01,000
I'm here to tell you—

121
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:05,840
follow your heart and leave no regrets.

122
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:35,570
♪ By the water, the moon's reflection
is faintly bright ♪

123
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:38,680
♪ Thin mist curls gently, light as smoke ♪

124
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:42,230
♪ Looking back at the old scenery
of days gone by ♪

125
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:45,170
♪ No trace in sight ♪

126
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:48,900
♪ Entangled with love ♪

127
00:13:49,850 --> 00:13:52,110
♪ Mending and patching a broken heart ♪

128
00:13:52,630 --> 00:13:53,270
Grandmaster,

129
00:13:52,950 --> 00:13:55,400
♪ The kiss still lingers on my lips ♪

130
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:55,840
Celestial Attendant Fan and Zhang Suan
request an audience.

131
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:56,630
Let them in.

132
00:13:56,550 --> 00:13:58,560
♪ Brilliant as the stars in the sky ♪

133
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:02,010
♪ I pretend to stroll with ease ♪

134
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:05,190
♪ Avoiding the gaze of your eyes ♪

135
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:08,140
♪ I'm already in tears, though ♪

136
00:14:09,210 --> 00:14:11,870
♪ Wetting a dragonfly in mid-flight ♪

137
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:14,650
Is His Lordship
really so seriously injured?

138
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:17,550
I was healing him
with my spiritual energy.

139
00:14:17,860 --> 00:14:20,180
His divine soul is almost utterly wrecked.

140
00:14:20,180 --> 00:14:21,750
Li Mo was telling the truth.

141
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:27,980
He only remembers you, Divine Lord.
That's interesting.

142
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:31,360
Guess you are the only one
he can't let go of.

143
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:37,330
Why did you come together?

144
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:39,030
Despite my depleted spiritual energy,

145
00:14:39,030 --> 00:14:41,560
I don't want to be
a burden on you, Divine Lord.

146
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:45,150
I've been delving into artifact forging
and formations the past few days.

147
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:49,280
I remember the Great Wilderness Stele
is still in your possession, right?

148
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:55,370
I've heard about
what happened the other day.

149
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:56,870
This Great Wilderness Stele is listed

150
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:59,800
in the Record of Artifacts
Xiao Jingshan gave to you.

151
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:02,910
According to my investigation,
unlike ordinary artifacts,

152
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:05,170
this item takes countless days to forge.

153
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,320
So I think this artifact must have been

154
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:09,380
forged by Xiao Jingshan for himself.

155
00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:11,150
By repairing the Great Wilderness Stele,

156
00:15:11,150 --> 00:15:13,010
we can rebuild the past illusion.

157
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,510
Perhaps it'll reveal

158
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:16,320
some clues about Xiao Jingshan.

159
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:20,150
I remember you said
you tried to activate the formation

160
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:22,380
remaining on it by all means but failed.

161
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,110
I can't activate it,

162
00:15:25,220 --> 00:15:26,750
but maybe he can pull it off.

163
00:15:28,210 --> 00:15:29,720
Zhang Suan's
current cultivation techniques

164
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,720
all belonged to Xiao Jingshan before.

165
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:32,650
Besides, he once entered

166
00:15:32,650 --> 00:15:34,670
the illusion you used
the Great Wilderness Stele to create.

167
00:15:34,670 --> 00:15:37,130
Based on my experience
in artifact forging,

168
00:15:37,270 --> 00:15:37,840
Zhang Suan

169
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:40,430
should be the real owner
of the Great Wilderness Stele now.

170
00:15:40,430 --> 00:15:41,530
Only he

171
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:44,250
can activate
the repairing formation on it.

172
00:15:46,210 --> 00:15:47,240
I can give it a try.

173
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:50,770
Then let's do it.

174
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,870
[Prosperity]

175
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,250
Channel your spiritual energy
into the pattern

176
00:16:02,250 --> 00:16:04,110
and guide it along the paths on it.

177
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,230
Look, Divine Lord!

178
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,970
It's really been repaired.

179
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:53,960
Ling'er, did you just say that
after the repair,

180
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:55,630
we could also restore the past illusion

181
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:57,830
created by the Great Wilderness Stele?

182
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:03,240
Are you okay to continue?

183
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:04,400
Sure.

184
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,089
Just tell me what to do.

185
00:17:08,660 --> 00:17:09,880
Just like before,

186
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,310
channel your spiritual energy
to the Great Wilderness Stele,

187
00:17:13,310 --> 00:17:15,569
follow the spiritual energy paths on it,

188
00:17:15,819 --> 00:17:18,950
find the past you want to see,
and conjure it up.

189
00:17:21,790 --> 00:17:24,660
Divine Lord,
my spiritual energy has been drained,

190
00:17:24,690 --> 00:17:26,960
so I can't enter
the Great Wilderness Stele.

191
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:28,400
Zhang Suan needs
to activate the formation,

192
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,880
so he can't enter the illusion either.

193
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:31,270
Are you ready to enter the illusion

194
00:17:31,270 --> 00:17:33,330
of the Great Wilderness Stele again?

195
00:17:34,990 --> 00:17:37,440
In the past, Xiao Jingshan was always
lurking in the dark

196
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:39,210
spying on our lives.

197
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:43,070
Now it's my turn to peep into his life.

198
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:47,840
Let's begin.

199
00:17:58,990 --> 00:17:59,800
Darling.

200
00:18:17,890 --> 00:18:18,630
Darling,

201
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:22,050
were you trying
to leave me behind again just now?

202
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:25,370
No.

203
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:29,310
Glad to hear that!

204
00:18:29,510 --> 00:18:32,170
Anyway, wherever you go,
I'm sticking with you.

205
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:43,270
Where are we?

206
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:44,830
Honey, I'm back.

207
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:45,570
Welcome back.

208
00:18:45,570 --> 00:18:47,460
Darling, where are you going?

209
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,880
How's Mr. Wei's leg?

210
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:50,410
He probably can walk without his crutches

211
00:18:50,410 --> 00:18:51,750
in a couple of days.

212
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:54,480
He was just saying that
we don't need to bring him meals anymore.

213
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:57,240
Here you are. He fell over and got hurt
while hunting with you.

214
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:58,920
Besides, he lives alone.

215
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:00,960
We should show more concern for him.

216
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:03,210
Yes, you're right, honey.

217
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,140
Time to eat!

218
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:07,890
Come on, Baby Bean,
you must be hungry. Come here.

219
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:10,090
Dad!

220
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,290
Good boy.

221
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:13,830
Father, Mother, lunch's ready!

222
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:14,570
-Coming.
-Okay.

223
00:19:14,570 --> 00:19:15,500
Take your seats.

224
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:17,400
Baby Bean, hand out the chopsticks.

225
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:17,870
Here.

226
00:19:17,910 --> 00:19:18,830
Darling.

227
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:19,830
Sit properly.

228
00:19:19,830 --> 00:19:21,490
Why do you keep looking at him?

229
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:22,720
-Yes, I missed you.
-Good boy.

230
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:23,720
Look at me.

231
00:19:23,750 --> 00:19:25,550
Did you behave yourself at home?

232
00:19:25,770 --> 00:19:27,010
Look at me.

233
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:29,500
He's been very well-behaved.

234
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:35,550
-Baby Bean's grown up.
-Thanks.

235
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:37,280
He can hand out chopsticks now.

236
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:37,640
Good.

237
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:38,440
Thank you.

238
00:19:40,510 --> 00:19:41,240
Here you are.

239
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:44,430
Jingshan, has Mr. Wei's leg
gotten any better?

240
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:47,100
Mr. Wei's leg will recover
in just a few days.

241
00:19:49,010 --> 00:19:49,810
Come on, let's eat.

242
00:19:49,810 --> 00:19:52,890
Darling, are you hungry too?

243
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:54,250
Come on, have some more.

244
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:55,950
Here you are, Mother.

245
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:57,440
What are you eating?

246
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:59,790
-Share some with Baby Bean.
-Okay.

247
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:01,110
I'm talking to you!

248
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:02,550
Eat some more meat.

249
00:20:02,550 --> 00:20:03,590
Mother, keep it to yourself.

250
00:20:03,590 --> 00:20:04,550
That's weird.

251
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:07,290
Why do they seem like they can't see us?

252
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:08,440
Tastes good, huh?

253
00:20:09,310 --> 00:20:10,310
Here, Baby Bean.

254
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:11,210
Give it a try.

255
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:12,870
Try it.

256
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:18,290
Dad, don't forget that you promised

257
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:20,200
to take me to the lantern fair tonight.

258
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:22,310
I want to light lanterns
and watch acrobatics.

259
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:23,400
Come back home early.

260
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:25,710
Alright, I won't forget.

261
00:20:26,110 --> 00:20:26,710
Come here.

262
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:28,470
Take it slow.

263
00:20:28,470 --> 00:20:29,470
I'm leaving then.

264
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:30,650
Come back early.

265
00:20:30,830 --> 00:20:32,000
Goodbye, Dad.

266
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,550
This is not what I expected.

267
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:40,120
Let's go.

268
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:44,550
Darling,

269
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,540
why do you keep staring at him?

