Lanterns for sale, take a look!

275
00:21:12,860 --> 00:21:13,980
Look over here!

276
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:18,090
Look! Look!

277
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,440
Beautiful.

278
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:22,070
So pretty.

279
00:21:22,510 --> 00:21:25,110
Hurry up, or we'll be late.

280
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:26,150
Alright!

281
00:21:28,240 --> 00:21:30,310
Nice!

282
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,170
Bravo!

283
00:21:35,310 --> 00:21:35,960
This one.

284
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:43,240
Bravo! Bravo! Brilliant!

285
00:21:45,070 --> 00:21:45,750
Do another one.

286
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:48,510
Bravo!

287
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,190
Nice!

288
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:53,990
Bravo!

289
00:21:54,010 --> 00:21:54,760
Amazing.

290
00:21:57,750 --> 00:21:58,370
Bravo!

291
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,550
Bravo! Bravo!

292
00:21:59,550 --> 00:22:01,070
-One more!
-One more!

293
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:02,920
Do another one.

294
00:22:02,940 --> 00:22:03,550
Awesome!

295
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:07,310
Bravo!

296
00:22:09,510 --> 00:22:12,060
Darling, do you like this too?

297
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:13,340
I can do the same trick!

298
00:22:15,420 --> 00:22:17,280
I want to go over there.

299
00:22:17,300 --> 00:22:17,720
Let's go.

300
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,960
Come on, let's go.

301
00:22:23,340 --> 00:22:23,860
Bravo!

302
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:25,860
Nice!

303
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:29,550
Look.

304
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:30,540
It's moving!

305
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:33,770
Which one do you like?

306
00:22:33,770 --> 00:22:34,350
This one.

307
00:22:34,350 --> 00:22:35,400
You like this one?

308
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:35,880
Okay.

309
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:37,840
Be careful.

310
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:38,890
Take it slow.

311
