-Be careful.
-Stay safe.

312
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:44,070
Lanterns.

313
00:22:44,070 --> 00:22:45,720
Take a look!

314
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:46,350
Darling.

315
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:49,750
Check these lanterns out!

316
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:00,020
Honey.

317
00:23:03,460 --> 00:23:04,920
Hey, people are watching.

318
00:23:06,970 --> 00:23:10,710
Xiao Jingshan, why on earth did you create

319
00:23:11,640 --> 00:23:12,880
this illusion?

320
00:23:17,990 --> 00:23:20,520
This lantern we bought today
is so beautiful.

321
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:33,960
Do you like it?

322
00:23:37,770 --> 00:23:40,370
I saw you staring
at the lantern he was holding.

323
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:42,480
So I conjured one up.

324
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:44,720
Do you like it?

325
00:23:59,000 --> 00:23:59,640
Darling,

326
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:04,050
are you still mad at me
for being talkative?

327
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:06,040
Why aren't you even smiling?

328
00:24:15,130 --> 00:24:16,330
Darling, you smiled!

329
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,510
My darling smiled!

330
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,780
You look so beautiful when you smile.

331
00:24:21,950 --> 00:24:23,210
Give me another smile.

332
00:24:25,050 --> 00:24:25,930
Gorgeous.

333
00:24:27,070 --> 00:24:28,140
Bai Jiusi,

334
00:24:29,070 --> 00:24:30,950
how am I supposed to deal with you?

335
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:37,260
Why is it morning again?

336
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:43,220
What happened? Did I miss something?

337
00:24:46,030 --> 00:24:47,480
Honey, I'm home.

338
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,330
Welcome back.

339
00:24:49,570 --> 00:24:50,970
How's Mr. Wei's leg?

340
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:52,440
He probably can walk without his crutches

341
00:24:52,440 --> 00:24:53,970
in a couple of days.

342
00:24:54,310 --> 00:24:56,880
He was just saying that
we don't need to bring him meals anymore.

343
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:59,590
Here you are. He fell over and got hurt
while hunting with you.

344
00:24:59,590 --> 00:25:01,310
Besides, he lives alone.

345
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:03,240
We should show more concern for him.

346
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:05,460
Yes, you're right, honey.

347
00:25:06,790 --> 00:25:07,450
Time to eat!

348
00:25:07,510 --> 00:25:10,240
Come on, Baby Bean,
you must be hungry. Come here.

349
00:25:10,550 --> 00:25:11,270
Why do they

350
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:13,200
keep repeating the same old lines?

351
00:25:16,380 --> 00:25:16,880
Dad!

352
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,040
Good boy.

353
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:20,450
Father, Mother, lunch's ready!

354
00:25:20,450 --> 00:25:21,700
Okay, coming!

355
00:25:22,930 --> 00:25:24,930
Baby Bean, hand out the chopsticks.

356
00:25:26,270 --> 00:25:27,070
Sit properly.

357
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:29,310
Baby Bean's grown up.

358
00:25:29,310 --> 00:25:30,480
He can hand out chopsticks now.

359
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:32,240
Did you behave yourself at home?

360
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:33,750
Did you listen to your mother?

361
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:35,810
-He's been very well-behaved.
-Yes.

362
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:38,400
Today's lunch is delicious.

363
00:25:38,430 --> 00:25:39,770
Then have some more.

364
00:25:40,590 --> 00:25:44,200
Is this illusion just repeating itself?

365
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:45,790
-Mother, have some more.
-Here, Baby Bean.

366
00:25:45,790 --> 00:25:46,480
Okay.

367
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:49,090
Dad, don't forget that you promised

368
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:51,110
to take me to the lantern fair tonight.

369
00:25:51,110 --> 00:25:53,350
I want to light lanterns
and watch acrobatics.

370
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:54,350
Come back home early.

371
00:25:54,350 --> 00:25:56,720
Alright, I won't forget.

372
00:25:56,940 --> 00:25:57,540
Come here.

373
00:25:59,070 --> 00:25:59,510
Take it slow.

374
00:25:59,510 --> 00:26:00,510
I'm leaving then.

375
00:26:00,590 --> 00:26:01,400
Come back early.

376
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:02,350
Goodbye, Dad.

377
00:26:05,510 --> 00:26:06,040
Let's go.

378
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,580
It's time to go.

379
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:17,680
Where to?

380
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:32,110
Divine Lord, you're back so soon.

381
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:33,310
Did you discover anything?

382
00:26:33,310 --> 00:26:35,590
In that illusion, there's only one day

383
00:26:36,060 --> 00:26:37,320
that keeps repeating.

384
00:26:39,070 --> 00:26:40,400
So you mean

385
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,590
Xiao Jingshan used
the Great Wilderness Stele

386
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:44,720
to create an illusion of a certain day,

387
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:47,360
and he's been living
the same day over and over?

388
00:26:47,360 --> 00:26:48,160
That's right.

389
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:50,930
Anything special about that day?

390
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:53,130
I found nothing special.

391
00:26:53,590 --> 00:26:56,550
It's just Xiao Jingshan's daily life
with his family.

392
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:59,420
But I guess his inner struggle
might lie there.

393
00:27:01,270 --> 00:27:03,440
Xiao Jingshan spent
a whole lot of time getting to know

394
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:06,070
Bai Jiusi and me
and turning us against each other,

395
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:07,730
which gave him the upper hand.

396
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,680
Now his advantage is gone.

397
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:13,010
I'll go check it out in Wenxuan Palace.

398
00:27:14,110 --> 00:27:15,040
I'll go with you.

399
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,300
You need to rest now.

400
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:25,640
Your going along would only
drag the Divine Lord down.

401
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:29,550
I'm starting to believe that

402
00:27:29,550 --> 00:27:32,680
Heavenly Lord Dacheng's
having a problem with his mind.

403
00:27:32,890 --> 00:27:34,890
Otherwise, given his personality,

404
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:36,400
how could he possibly condescend

405
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:38,330
to keep pestering the Divine Lord?

406
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:41,350
This symptom

407
00:27:42,750 --> 00:27:45,750
has actually given him
a chance to ease their tension.

408
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:50,770
Zhang Suan.

409
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:54,280
Let me remind you once again.

410
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:56,640
Don't forget that they are married.

411
00:28:01,830 --> 00:28:02,750
So what?

412
00:28:04,690 --> 00:28:10,670
♪ Pressing to my ear, brushing slowly ♪

413
00:28:11,420 --> 00:28:17,380
♪ Heartbeat drowns out
the quickened breathing ♪

414
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:29,400
♪ Intertwined, we burn ♪

415
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:26,010
Destiny of marriage...

416
00:28:29,690 --> 00:28:31,420
Wonder if it's really a destiny

417
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:33,660
or a calamity.

418
00:29:00,510 --> 00:29:05,090
All beings emerge in this world,
either good or evil,

419
00:29:05,330 --> 00:29:07,870
visible or hidden.

420
00:29:08,670 --> 00:29:11,330
Where there are gods, there are demons.

421
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:14,430
Demons grow from the darkness
in human hearts.

422
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:16,630
As long as life goes on,

423
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:19,070
demons will never vanish.

424
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:23,690
A thought can beget compassion
as well as evil.

425
00:29:23,980 --> 00:29:28,690
Evil rises from the depths of the heart,
manifesting in the Five Sufferings.

426
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:31,160
Greed.

427
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:38,200
Wrath.

428
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:40,480
So expensive! There are even worms on it!

429
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:41,000
Who would buy it?

430
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:41,880
Worms? Where?

431
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:42,790
Are you blind?

432
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:43,440
Why did you hit me?

433
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:44,810
Screw you!

434
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:47,250
How unreasonable you are!

435
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:49,240
[Prosperous Casino]

436
00:29:48,110 --> 00:29:48,830
Obsession.

437
00:29:49,800 --> 00:29:52,650
Son, you can't go!

438
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:53,760
Leave me alone!

439
00:29:55,510 --> 00:29:57,160
Son, let's go home.

440
00:29:55,930 --> 00:29:59,270
[Prosperous Casino]

441
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:59,590
You've raised a son for nothing.

442
00:29:59,590 --> 00:30:00,030
Arrogance.

443
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:00,600
Let go!

444
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,640
Please give me some.

445
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:02,550
-Hands off.
-Just a little.

446
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:03,480
-Go away!
-Please!

447
00:30:03,480 --> 00:30:05,010
You would never let go, huh?

448
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:07,750
I'm begging you.

449
00:30:07,750 --> 00:30:08,510
Suspicion.

450
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:09,240
My love.

451
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:10,030
Babe.

452
00:30:16,370 --> 00:30:17,700
Come and try this, babe.

453
00:30:17,750 --> 00:30:19,300
I bought these cakes
especially for you.

454
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:20,900
They're all your favorites.

455
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:45,510
The Five Sufferings give rise to demons
as obstacles for all living beings.

456
00:30:53,650 --> 00:30:54,550
Here, here!

457
00:30:57,300 --> 00:30:58,430
My Lord.

458
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:04,380
Darling, come up here
and join us in the fun.

459
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:09,750
My Lord!

460
00:31:12,790 --> 00:31:13,960
Still haven't found it?

461
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:14,640
I got it!

462
00:31:30,510 --> 00:31:32,570
The family of four you're looking for

463
00:31:33,510 --> 00:31:34,640
died on the same day.

464
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:35,490
Which day?

465
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:40,710
The day when Lord Qing Xu
eliminated the Lei Bird.

466
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:43,360
It was Lord Qing Xu again?

467
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:46,290
What exactly happened in that battle?

468
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:47,570
600 years ago,

469
00:31:47,790 --> 00:31:50,880
Lord Qing Xu, Yuan Chenghua,
led the celestial army to hunt down

470
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:53,310
the Lei Bird that was
wreaking havoc on the mortal realm.

471
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:55,640
He struck Nanwu Village
with celestial fire.

472
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:58,350
Twelve armored celestial soldiers
died in this battle.

473
00:31:58,350 --> 00:32:01,160
Five mortals in the mortal realm
were caught up in it

474
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,580
and burned to death.

475
00:32:04,510 --> 00:32:07,680
You vile creature!
You have nowhere to run!

476
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:38,830
Mr. Wei, your leg hasn't fully healed yet.

477
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:40,120
Why are you out here?

478
00:32:40,440 --> 00:32:41,360
Father!

479
00:33:12,290 --> 00:33:14,550
Dad, don't forget that you promised

480
00:33:14,550 --> 00:33:16,440
to take me to the lantern fair tonight.

481
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:18,720
I want to light lanterns
and watch acrobatics.

482
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:20,280
Come back home early.

483
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:25,860
Baby Bean! Baby Bean!

484
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,900
Honey.

485
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:32,880
Father! Mother!

486
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:37,040
Wake up, Baby Bean!

487
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,350
No.

488
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:10,610
Let me give it a shot.

489
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:15,810
When I first met Xiao Jingshan,

490
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:16,920
he did tell me that

491
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:19,040
he cultivated to seek revenge in heaven.

492
00:34:19,040 --> 00:34:20,840
But after he ascended to the Nine Heavens,

493
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:23,170
he learned that
the guy had died in battle.

494
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:24,670
So...

495
00:34:24,670 --> 00:34:25,750
Bai Jiusi!

496
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:30,330
Xiao Jingshan insisted
on destroying the Infinite Stele

497
00:34:28,420 --> 00:34:31,610
[Prosperity]

498
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:33,440
just to erase the name on it.

499
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:35,190
That should be it.

500
00:34:36,150 --> 00:34:38,360
I've heard that the names
engraved on the Infinite Stele

501
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:41,440
are all divine race generals who perished
in the war between gods and demons,

502
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,840
including Lord Qing Xu.

503
00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:46,440
He plunged all the Three Realms

504
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:49,409
into peril just to wipe out a name?

505
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:54,480
Losing loved ones can indeed
drive a person crazy.

506
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:58,300
I, too, once lost it and went astray.

507
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:01,030
Xiao Jingshan lost

508
00:35:01,030 --> 00:35:02,890
all his loved ones in a single day.

509
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:05,440
Lord Qing Xu must have
become his obsession.

510
00:35:08,190 --> 00:35:11,450
Grandmaster, you didn't drag
any innocent people into it.

511
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:13,850
We've all been following you willingly.

512
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:21,800
Now that we know Xiao Jingshan's past,

513
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:23,480
all that's left is to

514
00:35:24,110 --> 00:35:26,280
find him and stop him.

515
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:27,800
Yes.

516
00:35:29,510 --> 00:35:30,000
Yes.

517
00:35:58,970 --> 00:36:01,820
♪ By the water, the moon's reflection
is faintly bright ♪

518
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:05,290
♪ Thin mist curls gently, light as smoke ♪

519
00:36:05,990 --> 00:36:08,510
♪ Looking back at the old scenery
of days gone by ♪

520
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:11,680
♪ No trace in sight ♪

521
00:36:12,340 --> 00:36:15,280
♪ Entangled with love ♪

522
00:36:16,090 --> 00:36:18,500
♪ Mending and patching a broken heart ♪

523
00:36:19,190 --> 00:36:21,640
♪ The kiss still lingers on my lips ♪

524
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:24,860
♪ Brilliant as the stars in the sky ♪

525
00:36:25,780 --> 00:36:28,080
♪ I pretend to stroll with ease ♪

526
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:31,520
♪ Avoiding the gaze of your eyes ♪

527
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:34,610
♪ I'm already in tears, though ♪

528
00:36:35,300 --> 00:36:38,120
♪ Wetting a dragonfly in mid-flight ♪

529
00:36:39,230 --> 00:36:41,550
♪ I wish I could ♪

530
00:36:40,670 --> 00:36:44,280
[Time-traveling Sundial]

531
00:36:42,330 --> 00:36:46,230
♪ Travel back to the past ♪

532
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:47,400
The Resurrection Formation,
Great Wilderness Stele,

533
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:49,060
and Time-traveling Sundial.

534
00:36:50,710 --> 00:36:51,640
Xiao Jingshan,

535
00:36:53,150 --> 00:36:55,680
you forged them all
for yourself, didn't you?

536
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:06,360
Who's so ill-mannered
to visit in the dead of night?

537
00:37:13,550 --> 00:37:17,550
I've long heard about the Yinlian Sect's
disdain for manners and rules.

538
00:37:18,090 --> 00:37:20,500
Are those rumors

539
00:37:21,510 --> 00:37:22,510
incorrect?

540
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:26,600
We can be rude to you,

541
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:29,740
but that doesn't mean
you can disrespect us.

542
00:37:35,670 --> 00:37:36,980
Your Yinlian Sect

543
00:37:37,110 --> 00:37:38,800
starts to grow on me.

544
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:40,970
Who on earth are you?

545
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:44,420
My identity is not important.

546
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:47,920
I came here today to make a deal with you.

547
00:37:49,550 --> 00:37:50,400
A deal on what?

548
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:54,710
Many sects here claim to be righteous

549
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:59,000
and call the Yinlian Sect
an evil demonic sect.

550
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:03,960
Don't you want to eradicate those who

551
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:05,440
look down on you?

552
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:09,860
No, I don't.

553
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:15,000
They call the Yinlian Sect
an evil demonic sect

554
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:17,850
because we are unrestrained

555
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:19,490
and don't play by the rules.

556
00:38:20,030 --> 00:38:21,830
But that doesn't mean we're bad.

557
00:38:23,150 --> 00:38:24,970
You just seem to be up to no good.

558
00:38:26,710 --> 00:38:28,840
I won't join hands with you, of course.

559
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:31,180
Never mind.

560
00:38:32,630 --> 00:38:35,160
I didn't intend to negotiate
with you anyway.

561
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:24,140
So hideous!

562
00:39:24,470 --> 00:39:26,000
D-Don't come any closer!

563
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:32,470
How many times have I told you

564
00:39:32,470 --> 00:39:33,930
not to bully His Lordship?

565
00:39:34,630 --> 00:39:36,460
Alright, alright, I got it.

566
00:39:36,590 --> 00:39:38,040
Untie me now.

567
00:39:38,150 --> 00:39:39,440
It's way too tight.

568
00:39:39,800 --> 00:39:42,130
That's what've you got for not listening.

569
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:03,060
All things thrive, and that is creation.

570
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:06,520
The world settles down,
and that is stability.

571
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:08,710
Gradual destruction is decay.

572
00:40:09,190 --> 00:40:11,360
Vanishing into nothing is void.

573
00:40:13,480 --> 00:40:16,080
Over 400 years ago,
I slayed the Drought Dragon

574
00:40:16,510 --> 00:40:18,710
and avoided the destructive calamity.

575
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:23,210
I didn't know it would still
be inevitable today.

576
00:40:25,230 --> 00:40:27,690
You're a spiritual beast
with a sharp sense.

577
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:33,070
You must've also sensed
the upcoming calamity, right?

578
00:41:01,900 --> 00:41:03,640
[Don't come back.]

579
00:41:07,350 --> 00:41:08,650
[Don't come back.]

580
00:41:41,560 --> 00:41:42,860
Immortal Lord, something terrible

581
00:41:42,860 --> 00:41:44,390
happened at the Hell Ruins!

582
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:01,400
Greetings, Sect Leader.

583
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:06,650
D-Did anything happen?

584
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:12,760
Yin Tongzi is just a child.

585
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,110
Why are you afraid of him?

586
00:42:14,110 --> 00:42:15,770
He threatened to eat me alive.

587
00:42:23,230 --> 00:42:23,890
Go have fun.

588
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,330
Grandmaster.

589
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:29,450
Go.

590
00:42:38,070 --> 00:42:39,550
What brought you back here?

591
00:42:39,550 --> 00:42:41,400
Have you found
Xiao Jingshan's whereabouts?

592
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:42,280
I came here

593
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:44,280
to report other important matters.

594
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:45,730
Recently, Dan Yang and I,

595
00:42:45,760 --> 00:42:48,880
along with other disciples,
have been searching everywhere.

596
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:51,070
We've discovered that
many people across the land

597
00:42:51,070 --> 00:42:52,450
have lost their souls.

598
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:54,860
Normally, when the soul leaves the body,

599
00:42:54,860 --> 00:42:55,960
the body dies immediately.

600
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:57,880
But lately, there have been
hundreds of these people

601
00:42:57,880 --> 00:42:59,280
falling into a coma first

602
00:42:59,550 --> 00:43:00,950
and dying in their dreams

603
00:43:01,030 --> 00:43:02,630
on the fifth day.

604
00:43:03,550 --> 00:43:05,560
Today is already the third day,

605
00:43:05,630 --> 00:43:07,070
and things are getting out of hand.

606
00:43:07,070 --> 00:43:09,760
So I came to seek help
from you, Grandmaster.

607
00:43:10,030 --> 00:43:12,440
Any connection between the people
who lost their souls?

608
00:43:12,440 --> 00:43:13,950
Where did their souls go?

609
00:43:14,280 --> 00:43:16,190
They don't know each other.

610
00:43:16,670 --> 00:43:18,840
Some are even thousands of miles apart.

611
00:43:18,840 --> 00:43:19,710
I've sent the disciples

612
00:43:19,710 --> 00:43:22,590
everywhere to check
how many people have fallen into comas.

613
00:43:22,590 --> 00:43:24,320
I suspect that

614
00:43:25,150 --> 00:43:27,590
it might be Xiao Jingshan's doing.

615
00:43:28,440 --> 00:43:30,500
The Great Wilderness Stele he forged

616
00:43:30,600 --> 00:43:33,400
can capture
the primordial spirits of immortals.

617
00:43:33,440 --> 00:43:36,590
Now, he must have made
another magical artifact

618
00:43:36,590 --> 00:43:38,720
that can capture the souls of mortals.

619
00:43:39,360 --> 00:43:42,220
Capturing mortal souls
in such a high-profile way,

620
00:43:42,710 --> 00:43:44,040
what on earth is he up to?

621
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:46,110
Xingman, Xingman.

622
00:43:46,130 --> 00:43:47,000
Li Qingyue!

623
00:43:48,110 --> 00:43:49,900
Mind your attitude
to our grandmaster.

624
00:43:49,900 --> 00:43:51,760
Does your Jingyun Sect
have any available manpower

625
00:43:51,760 --> 00:43:53,870
to go back with me to the Yinlian Sect?

626
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:55,030
What happened to your sect again?

627
00:43:55,030 --> 00:43:56,710
My mother sent a message through a raven,

628
00:43:56,710 --> 00:43:57,960
telling me not to go back.

629
00:43:57,960 --> 00:43:59,580
No way she'd say that

630
00:43:59,740 --> 00:44:01,740
unless something hit our sect hard.

631
00:44:03,540 --> 00:44:04,460
Li Qingyue,

632
00:44:04,670 --> 00:44:06,270
you can't ignore my trouble.

633
00:44:06,360 --> 00:44:07,880
When the Jingyun Sect was in chaos,

634
00:44:07,880 --> 00:44:10,210
I also stood by you
through thick and thin!

635
00:44:10,870 --> 00:44:11,650
Xingman,

636
00:44:12,250 --> 00:44:14,230
we don't know what's really going on yet.

637
00:44:14,230 --> 00:44:15,230
Calm down first.

638
00:44:15,230 --> 00:44:15,800
That's my mother.

639
00:44:15,800 --> 00:44:17,390
How can I calm down?

640
00:44:27,750 --> 00:44:29,320
Did anything happen in your place as well?

641
00:44:29,320 --> 00:44:31,230
I just received a message
from Senior Long Yuan,

642
00:44:31,230 --> 00:44:33,550
saying that the seal of the Hell Ruins
loosened for no reason.

643
00:44:33,550 --> 00:44:34,840
The demonic beasts imprisoned inside

644
00:44:34,840 --> 00:44:35,950
have all escaped.

645
00:44:36,550 --> 00:44:38,670
Divine Lord, please accommodate
our Heavenly Lord for a few more days.

646
00:44:38,670 --> 00:44:42,530
We need to return to Canglei Palace
to help subdue the demonic beasts.

647
00:44:46,070 --> 00:44:48,280
So it's really Xiao Jingshan
behind all these issues.

648
00:44:48,280 --> 00:44:50,030
He's been plotting for quite a while.

649
00:44:50,030 --> 00:44:52,280
He knows he stands no chance
in a head-on fight.

650
00:44:52,280 --> 00:44:53,880
So he's trying to split us up.

651
00:44:54,550 --> 00:44:55,800
I'll keep an eye on Bai Jiusi

652
00:44:55,800 --> 00:44:57,230
and keep him safe and sound.

653
00:44:57,230 --> 00:44:59,070
You can go back to Canglei Palace.

654
00:44:59,070 --> 00:45:00,400
Thank you, Divine Lord.

655
00:45:05,010 --> 00:45:07,920
[Prosperity]

656
00:45:07,320 --> 00:45:08,000
Zi Yang,

657
00:45:08,150 --> 00:45:10,000
you go to Yinlian Sect with Qu Xingman.

658
00:45:10,000 --> 00:45:11,110
I'll go with Dan Yang

659
00:45:11,110 --> 00:45:13,760
to see what's going on
with those mortals who lost their souls.

660
00:45:13,760 --> 00:45:14,820
Yes, Grandmaster.

661
00:45:16,320 --> 00:45:16,920
Darling,

662
00:45:17,550 --> 00:45:18,750
you can't move alone.

663
00:45:18,950 --> 00:45:20,000
I must go with you.

664
00:45:25,440 --> 00:45:27,550
We don't know if the Life-Link Curse
has been removed yet.

665
00:45:27,550 --> 00:45:29,060
If Xiao Jingshan shows up,

666
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:30,360
don't kill him.

667
00:45:30,440 --> 00:45:31,960
Catch him alive if possible.

668
00:45:31,960 --> 00:45:33,920
I'll leave Xuan Wei at Jingyun Sect.

669
00:45:33,920 --> 00:45:35,630
When you can no longer handle it,

670
00:45:35,630 --> 00:45:36,830
avoid confrontation

671
00:45:36,840 --> 00:45:39,760
and send a message
to ask Xuan Wei for reinforcements.

672
00:45:39,760 --> 00:45:40,920
There's no time to waste.

673
00:45:40,920 --> 00:45:42,000
Let's split up and move.
